(6, 'CEW BEAUTY AWARDS EDIT: WHAT YOU NEED TO KNOW', 'SOLO-BOX-1548x90336.jpg', 'The CEW Beauty Awards Edit will put the spotlight on award-nominated brands including ELEMIS, Iconic London, Omorovicza, Face Halo, Color Wow, Paula’s Choice, Code8 and more. Here’s what you need to know ahead of launch!\r\nThis exclusive Build Your Own Box edit will feature 35 products, across a range of nominated brands.\r\n\r\nThe CEW Beauty Awards Edit will go on sale at 7am on 19th February 2020.\r\n\r\nYou’ll be able to select 6 products from the shortlist, for just £24.\r\n\r\nSubscribers can take £5 OFF until Sunday (23rd February) with code CEWSUB\r\n\r\nIf you’re not subscribed, delivery is on us with code CEWFPP (until 23rd February)\r\n\r\nThe first 500 people to create a CEW Beauty Awards Edit will receive a FREE sample of the QMS Medicosmetics Epigen Depuff Pollution Shield Eye Serum.\r\n\r\nThere is no limit on the number of edits you can create.\r\n\r\nAll items will be added to the site at once, once they’re sold out, they are gone. Products will not be restocked. Items can also not be swapped once ordered.\r\n\r\nThere is limited stock, so if you see an item you really want, we urge you to get it ASAP.\r\n\r\nUnfortunately we are unable to reserve any items.\r\nGET READY. It’s going to be a busy one so please bear with us. If you’re having any issues with your basket, this could mean that one or more items have sold out while in your basket. Please do try the following before contacting customer service:\r\n\r\nEmpty your basket, close down the page, then try and clear your cookies, history and cache before accessing the site and trying again.<div>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Sint natus, magnam illo cum fuga deserunt voluptas atque nostrum incidunt! Delectus culpa ipsa nobis quas ducimus ea, soluta eaque doloremque ullam.</div>\r\n<div>Doloremque expedita repellat quasi culpa officiis inventore qui distinctio quia amet mollitia illum nesciu